'''Spice-jackers''' were [[Pirate/Legends|pirates]] who specialized in stealing loads of [[Spice/Legends|spice]] from other pirates, [[Smuggler/Legends|smugglers]], and merchants. [[Jak Sazz]], [[Romort Raort]], [[Elaginn]], and the [[Elaginn gang]] were all spice-jackers.

